traits.locale_text: "Я больше не буду тратить время и силы на поиски мятежников. В варп это расследование — у меня довольно иных дел".

languages.text: "I am not going to waste any more time or effort trying to find the mutineers. To the void with this investigation — I have enough to deal with as it is."
languages.original_text: "Я больше не буду тратить время и силы на поиски мятежников. В варп это расследование — у меня довольно иных дел".

traits.locale_text: "Precisely so. One day, they will crawl out of the shadows, and I will destroy them without resorting to rituals of any kind."

languages.text: «No voy a desperdiciar más tiempo ni esfuerzos en buscar amotinados. Al vacío con esta investigación; ya tengo bastante de lo que preocuparme».
languages.original_text: "I am not going to waste any more time or effort trying to find the mutineers. To the void with this investigation — I have enough to deal with as it is."

traits.locale_text: «Precisamente. Llegará un día en que saldrán de las sombras y los destruiré sin necesidad de rituales».

languages.text: 「反乱軍を探すためにこれ以上の時間や労力を浪費するつもりはない。この調査は無駄骨だった。ただでさえ、対処するべきことが多々というのに」
languages.original_text: "I am not going to waste any more time or effort trying to find the mutineers. To the void with this investigation — I have enough to deal with as it is."

traits.locale_text: 「そうだな。いずれ奴らが影から這い出たとき、儀式などなくとも{mf|俺|私}が奴らを葬ってくれよう」

languages.text: “我不打算继续浪费时间和精力搜查那些叛乱分子了。让调查什么的统统见鬼去吧，我要操心的事情已经够多了。”
languages.original_text: "I am not going to waste any more time or effort trying to find the mutineers. To the void with this investigation — I have enough to deal with as it is."

traits.locale_text: “没错，你说得对。总有一天，那些叛乱分子会从阴影里爬出来，而我会把他们连根铲除。我们不需要举行什么仪式。”

languages.text: "Ich werde keine Zeit mehr mit der Suche nach den Meuterern vergeuden. In die Leere mit dieser Untersuchung ... ich habe schon genug zu tun."
languages.original_text: "I am not going to waste any more time or effort trying to find the mutineers. To the void with this investigation — I have enough to deal with as it is."

traits.locale_text: "Genauso ist es. Eines Tages werden sie aus den Schatten kriechen, und ich werde sie ohne irgendein Ritual vernichten."

languages.text: « Je refuse de perdre plus de temps à tenter de débusquer les autres mutins. Que le vide emporte cette enquête. J'ai déjà bien assez à gérer comme ça. »
languages.original_text: "I am not going to waste any more time or effort trying to find the mutineers. To the void with this investigation — I have enough to deal with as it is."

traits.locale_text: « Précisément. Un jour, ils sortiront des ombres et je les détruirai sans qu'il soit besoin d'accomplir un quelconque rituel. »

languages.text: "İsyancıları bulmak için daha fazla zaman ya da çaba harcamayacağım. Böyle soruşturmayı uçsuz alsın. Zaten işim başımdan aşkın."
languages.original_text: "I am not going to waste any more time or effort trying to find the mutineers. To the void with this investigation — I have enough to deal with as it is."
